<v Speaker 2>Me enamoro de él.

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:27.800
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.880
<v Speaker 1>Me enamoro de él.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:34.280
<v Speaker 1>If we want to give the meaning of I'm falling in love right now

00:03:34.500 --> 00:03:39.620
<v Speaker 1>We can say I am, how is I am from a star?

